metadata.name: 01_Yukionna
metadata.description:
Yuki-Onna no Tsurara serves cold sweet dishes at Ayakashido.
The sweet treats she makes are so intensely cold and sweet that one bite can make you forget the heat, and they are so popular that they run out of stock in the summer.
Although she has no facial expression, she has a very calm and gentle personality and has many hidden fans.

雪女の氷柱は妖堂で冷たい甘味を提供している。
彼女の作る甘味は、一口で暑さを忘れるくらい強烈に冷たく、そして甘く、夏になると品切れになってしまうくらい人気だ。
無表情だが、とても穏やかで優しい性格をしており、隠れファンも多い。
